column6: Estimates are based on monthly Twitter data, using a custom lexicon to message unigrams.
We standardized estimates based on all prior time series data (M = 0.145 / SD = 0.0215), maintaining difference between the groups.
Customer lexicon: S. Kiritchenko, X. Zhu, S. M. Mohammad, Sentiment analysis of short informal texts. J. Artif. Intell. Res. 50, 723–762 (2014).
